something fucking epic!

15:29.095 --> 15:33.058
This is my fucking
moment in life!

15:33.099 --> 15:39.272
I want to get lost in-in wine
and strange lands and strangers.

15:39.314 --> 15:43.109
And I want to be
the fucking crazy one, for once.

15:43.151 --> 15:44.736
I want to be
the fucking crazy one!

15:44.778 --> 15:46.154
And I don't want to give a shit

15:46.196 --> 15:48.406
about messing up
someone else's day!

15:48.448 --> 15:51.326
So long as it's in service
of my art!

15:51.368 --> 15:52.994
Whoa, what the fuck?
Cool down.

15:53.036 --> 15:56.247
Oh, my God, Lizzie, I wish
that you were really here.

15:56.289 --> 15:59.751
-You're losing your grip, dude.
-I'm so confused, man.

15:59.793 --> 16:02.462
Well, what's the problem?
I mean, he adores you.

16:02.504 --> 16:05.340
You have a great time together;
I mean, he cooks you breakfast.

16:05.382 --> 16:06.800
You teach him,
you learn from him.

16:06.841 --> 16:08.218
I mean, what more do you want?

16:08.259 --> 16:09.511
Nothing, not a thing.

16:09.552 --> 16:11.471
But it's not about him,
it's about me.

16:11.513 --> 16:13.598
-I'm losing myself.
-You're just scared.

16:13.640 --> 16:15.934
And you're leaning towards
a romantic cliché--

16:15.975 --> 16:17.852
that you can't be yourself
without being alone.

16:17.894 --> 16:19.562
I'll be ready
for someone else later.

16:19.604 --> 16:21.981
-Right now, I need to focus
on me.

16:22.023 --> 16:24.150
I mean, this is the moment
that matters, right?

16:24.192 --> 16:25.735
Ichi go ichi e?

16:25.777 --> 16:26.986
"One life, one opportunity."

16:27.028 --> 16:28.738
Oh, I know. I know.

16:28.780 --> 16:31.825
I mean, who else in the world is
more dynamic, more charismatic?

16:31.866 --> 16:34.411
Not to mention the great sex
I've heard you talk about.

16:34.452 --> 16:36.996
I mean, who do you have
more of a connection with,

16:37.038 --> 16:39.582
that's more engaging,
fun to be around,

16:39.624 --> 16:41.793
knowledgeable about music
and passionate about art?

16:41.835 --> 16:44.003
I mean, all the things
you want in your life.

16:44.045 --> 16:45.755
No one.

16:45.797 --> 16:48.883
I think that you should commit
in a deeper, crazier way.

16:48.925 --> 16:52.303
I think that that would be
daring and beautiful.

16:52.345 --> 16:54.305
You're right.

16:54.347 --> 16:56.808
If you wait too long,
he'll be gone.

16:56.850 --> 16:58.435
We belong together.

16:58.476 --> 17:00.228
ANA MARIA:
Charming thought.

17:00.270 --> 17:02.480
