gonna get him. Not fully.

17:02.522 --> 17:04.107
Go ahead, commit.

17:04.148 --> 17:06.233
Just don't expect
the same from him.

17:06.276 --> 17:08.903
Trust me, you're not his type.
You're like a pillow.

17:08.944 --> 17:11.156
-Okay. I'm just
talking to my friend right now.

17:11.196 --> 17:13.450
He needs the fire!

17:13.491 --> 17:16.578
-The fire of a deeper,
crazy love. -Okay.

17:16.618 --> 17:17.787
Like we had.

17:17.829 --> 17:18.997
Maybe still have.

17:19.038 --> 17:20.832
What are you saying?

17:20.874 --> 17:22.625
I'm saying you're
too much of a mouse.

17:22.666 --> 17:24.377
You're not crazy enough.

17:24.419 --> 17:25.962
Fuck you, you pretentious
fucking asshole.

17:26.003 --> 17:27.714
LIZZIE:
Yeah, fuck you.

17:27.756 --> 17:29.591
You got a problem with her,
you have a problem with me.

17:29.632 --> 17:31.885
If I hadn't taken
a vow of nonviolence...

17:31.926 --> 17:33.178
:
I still carry a knife.

17:33.219 --> 17:35.013
Hey, guys, guys. Hey. Hey.

17:35.054 --> 17:36.306
Hey.

17:36.347 --> 17:38.057
If you're not crazy already,

17:38.099 --> 17:40.769
if you stay with him, trust me,
he'll drive you crazy.

17:40.810 --> 17:42.771
Look at me.

17:42.812 --> 17:45.231
You make every woman who's
with you go a little insane.

17:45.273 --> 17:46.858
-No. Hai Lai,
don't listen to her.

17:46.900 --> 17:48.401
No, I'm not that kind
of person anymore.

17:49.736 --> 17:51.237
Come. I need
to tell you something.

17:51.279 --> 17:53.031
I'm sorry, Hai Lai.

17:53.072 --> 17:56.409
You were doing so well in the
competition and I messed you up.

17:56.451 --> 17:58.036
You should have won.

17:58.077 --> 18:01.122
No, I did it to myself. I froze.

18:01.164 --> 18:04.000
I just didn't want to be there,
and I couldn't be in the moment.

18:04.042 --> 18:06.377
And that's what
always happens to me.

18:06.419 --> 18:07.545
Always?

18:07.587 --> 18:08.713
Not always.

18:08.755 --> 18:10.673
Just when it really matters.

18:21.100 --> 18:23.520
AKI: So, now you ask,
"May I see the tea container

18:23.561 --> 18:25.855
and the tea scoop, please?"

18:25.897 --> 18:27.690
"Onatsume."
-Onatsume. -Onatsume.

18:27.732 --> 18:28.942
"Ocha shaku."

18:28.983 --> 18:30.401
-Ocha shaku.
-Ocha shaku.

18:30.443 --> 18:32.487
-"No haiken."
-No haiken. -No haiken.

18:32.529 --> 18:33.905
-AKI: "Onegai"
-Onegai. -Onegai.

18:33.947 --> 18:36.449
-AKI: Itashimas.
-Itashimas. -Itashimas.

18:38.952 --> 18:41.412
AKI: You may see
little hills and valleys,

18:41.454 --> 18:45.416
formed by the scoop
as it withdrew from the tea.

18:45.458 --> 18:48.169
It's like bamboo.

18:48.211 --> 18:51.339
From the forest.

18:51.381 --> 18:52.924
RODRIGO:
Hmm.

18:52.966 --> 18:55.385
AKI: This is why tea
takes a lifetime to master.

18:55.426 --> 18:57.387
Everything tells a story.

19:13.319 --> 19:15.738
Is this the real you, Hai Lai?

19:15.780 --> 19:17.782
Or it is me
just thinking about you?

19:17.824 --> 19:19.993
It's really me.

19:20.034 --> 19:24.080
There's so much things I've been
thinking about, recently.

19:24.122 --> 19:27.709
I feel I'm entering
a new perspective.

19:27.750 --> 19:30.712
I'm realizing new things
about myself.

19:30.753 --> 19:33.631
Me, too.

19:33.673 --> 19:36.134
There's so much
I want to tell you.

19:36.175 --> 19:38.887
Not now.

19:40.179 --> 19:43.266
Just be here with me.

19:43.308 --> 19:45.310
Just hold me.

19:53.401 --> 19:57.739
I never told you this,
with all my heart.

19:57.780 --> 20:00.033
I'm in love with you.

20:00.074 --> 20:03.244
I'm in love with you, too.

20:03.286 --> 20:05.288
Truly.

20:52.210 --> 20:55.171
Listen.

20:55.213 --> 20:57.173
It's the Concerto in C.

20:57.215 --> 21:00.385
You played it so beautifully.

21:00.426 --> 21:02.470
The day we met.

21:02.512 --> 21:06.516
A day I will never forget.

21:06.557 --> 21:09.519
♪ ♪

21:24.909 --> 21:27.078
-Hai Lai.
-Rodrigo.

21:27.120 --> 21:29.205
-I have to say something...
-I have something...

21:29.247 --> 21:30.415
Oh, well, uh, okay.

21:30.456 --> 21:31.624
You-you go first.

21:31.666 --> 21:33.126
No, it-- you go.

21:33.167 --> 21:34.585
Do... okay.

21:34.627 --> 21:36.170
We-we go--
both at the same time.

21:36.212 --> 21:38.006
-Okay.

21:38.047 --> 21:40.466
One, two, three.

21:40.508 --> 21:41.884
It's time for us to break up.

21:41.926 --> 21:43.928
I think we should have a family.

21:50.184 --> 21:54.981
AKI: There is one thing more
thing to say before we go.

21:55.023 --> 21:58.192
Shitsurei itashimasu.

21:58.234 --> 22:01.446
AKI: It means, "excuse me for
anything that wasn't perfect."

22:05.324 --> 22:07.869
I'm sorry.

